             SMS               2 and               SMS               1 are responsible for the synthesis of               SM               in the               PM               and endomembranes, respectively, in               COS               ‐1 cells. The use of the two               SM               ‐binding probes may provide more insights into various sphingomyelin‐mediated processes in different topological domains.},
